item.title: Paloma add a quote by Seth Grahame-Smith
item.description: "My sisters and I cannot spend any substantial time searching for Wickham, as we are each commanded by His Majesty to defend Hertfordshire from all enemies until such time as we are dead, rendered lame, or married." -- Seth Grahame-Smith

item.title: Paloma add a quote by E.L. Konigsburg
item.description: "If you think of doing something in New York City, you can be certain that at least two thousand other people have the same thought. And of the two thousand who do, about one thousand will be standing in line waiting to do it." -- E.L. Konigsburg
